data.description: Back to market at not fault of owner!  Short Sale in progress and approved.  Tri-Level property on Concord Schools District with a lot of space to enjoy country living.  Property is very close to churches, schools, supermarkets, gas stations, malls, and much more.  Master bedroom with walking closet and in-suite bathroom with a jacuzzi tub.  Kitchen is very spacious with an open concept.  Property is sold "as is".
